lyrics:
[Verse]
In the land where the sun always shines
Black, blue, and brown wolves intertwine
Under moons, their spirits align
Leaping and running, they howl, divine

[Chorus]
Black, blue, and brown wolves unite
Howling under the moonlit night
Their fusion of sounds takes flight
In a futuristic groove, pure delight
style: futuristic central American and south american hip hop pop fusion
